EIF.Label: Entry into force
EIF.Labeltext: 1 October 1992, in accordance with paragraphs 3, 4 and 5 of Resolution No. 355 adopted by the International Coffee Council on 27 September 1991. The Agreement was extended on 1 October 1993 by Resolution No. 363 adopted by the International Coffee Council on 4 June 1993 [see chapter XIX.25 g)].

TreatyText.Label: Text
TreatyText.Text: United Nations, Treaty Series, vol. 1691, p. 449; Resolution No. 355 adopted by the International Coffee Council.
